{
  "texts": [
    "However, research-related activities are certainly ripe for scientific scrutiny along the lines indicated in this study.",
    "Furthermore, only a limited set of institutions could be investigated, those who were the \"first respondents\" to the set of issues covered by this study.",
    "Hereby, this paper hopes to inspire further research on the impact of AI tools on higher education.",
    "Such research could cover more institutions, but it would also be interesting to revisit the same institutions again to see how their stance and approach might have changed over time considering how fast this technology evolves and how much we learn about its capabilities and shortcomings.",
    "Data sharing is not applicable to this article as no datasets were generated or analysed during the current study."
  ]
}